<p><b>How to write a brand collaboration proposal?</b> A brand collaboration proposal should be clear, persuasive, and backed with compelling evidence. Successful collaborations require thorough research of potential partners and careful planning. Proposals should include an introduction, goals and strategy, deliverables, timeline, expected results, and social proof.</p>
