<p><b>How to write a business proposal for a joint venture?</b> Craft a persuasive joint venture project proposal that clearly communicates the benefits, objectives, and expectations of the collaboration. Include an executive summary, project overview, deliverables, timeline, budget, and any other relevant information.</p>
